```', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2023, 10, 18, 10, 44, 44, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'surma', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 1363656567, 'comment_body': 'Memory leak here! See comment in encoder for explanation.
